title: Lynx capture 3rd title in 5 years with 69-52 win in Game 5
text:
> Sports Lynx capture 3rd title in 5 years with 69-52 win in Game 5 Minnesota Lynx's Lindsay Whalen, Maya Moore and Rebekkah Brunson celebrate their 69-52 victory over the Indiana Fever in Game 5 of the WNBA basketball finals, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015, in Minneapolis. (AP Photo/Stacy Bengs)
